cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MA, cs.SY

The paper deals with multi-agent interaction and learning algorithms, which are commonly studied in the sub-fields of game theory (cs.GT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of Dec-POMDPs also suggests a connection to the sub-field of multi-agent systems (cs.MA), while the focus on convergence to Nash equilibrium suggests a connection to control theory (cs.SY).
